Author: tulipsandmothballs
Text: See a dentist and be honest about purging. They might ask you to stop blah blah blah, but they can’t actually make you do anything if you are an adult. But if you can save your teeth you’ll be happier down the road.

Author: XSkeletonGirlX
Text: Part of me wishes I had more experience to help you out. At he very least though, I can say, try not to brush your teeth right after you purge. Ive been informed that it will fuck up your teeth more, and that its better to just rinse your mouth with water and wait at least half an hour till you brush them. If I cant help you get better, Ill at least try to help with some damage control.
